    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This vehicle is a prime example of pride of ownership, offering a fantastic blend of reliability and style. The exterior paint retains a deep, glossy finish, with only minor road-wear visible upon close inspection, typical of a car that has been enjoyed on the open road. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean and smoke-free; the seats show light, natural creasing but remain supportive and free of any punctures or tears. All onboard electronics, including the infotainment system and dual-zone climate control, function exactly as they should. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and quietly, benefiting from a documented history of on-time oil changes and recent brake service. The tires have plenty of tread remaining, and the suspension provides a firm yet comfortable ride without any unusual noises. This is a turn-key car that requires no immediate investment, perfect for someone who values a well-cared-for vehicle that looks and drives beautifully.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 49
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
