      "description": "We are pleased to offer this exceptionally well-maintained vehicle, presenting a refined balance of performance and value. This unit has been subjected to a rigorous multi-point inspection to ensure mechanical integrity and roadworthiness. Both the interior and exterior reflect a high standard of stewardship, showing only minor signs of careful previous ownership. It represents a premier opportunity for the professional seeking a reliable, high-caliber vehicle that performs with distinction.",
      "price": 34500.0,
